Deadpool and Wolverine Booty Controllers: Xbox, Why the Tease?

Ever dreamed of owning a limited edition controller featuring your favorite Marvel superheroes, Deadpool and Wolverine? Well, it seems Xbox had the same idea! But instead of making these bootylicious controllers available to the masses, they've left us hanging with a tantalizing tease. In this video, I'm diving deep into the world of Xbox's promotional tactics and expressing my disappointment over the lack of availability for these highly coveted controllers. Is this a strategic move, or just a cruel joke? Let's discuss!

@XBOX @VancityReynolds @marvel

#netflix #redcarpet #premiere 

Attended the black carpet premiere for Umbrella Academy season four. This is the final season, and the cool thing is that it's like a full circle moment for me. I also attended the season one premiere years ago, and it was cool. I’m glad to be here for the show's final season. Check it out! I did a bit of a vlog and then I’m sharing footage from the event using my Moment anamorphic lens, followed by a brief review of the first episode of season four, the final season of Umbrella Academy.

